SELECT 
            d.ts_code,
            s.name,
            d.close,
            d.pct_chg,
            d.vol,
            d.amount,
            b.turnover_rate,
            d.trade_date
        FROM tu_daily_detail d
        JOIN tu_stock_basic s ON d.ts_code = s.ts_code
        LEFT JOIN tu_daily_basic b ON d.ts_code = b.ts_code AND d.trade_date = b.trade_date
        WHERE d.ts_code = :ts_code
            AND d.trade_date = :trade_date
        LIMIT 1
